text: Sven Lidman is the name of: *Sven Lidman (clergyman) (1786–1845), clergyman, antiquarian and orientalist, dean of the cathedral of Linköping *Sven Lidman (writer) (1882–1960), writer, leading member of the Pentecostal movement in Sweden *Sven Lidman (lexicographer) (1921-2011), lexicographer
title: Sven Lidman
